					本所課程			










				  必修課程



				  碩士班



				‧應用數學 I 
Applied Mathematics I

				‧電子學實驗 
Experiments on Electronics

				‧應用力學實驗 I 
				 Experiments on Applied Mechanics I



				  One out of three courses below are also required:



				‧動力學 
Dynamics

				‧彈性力學 
				 Elasticity I

				‧流體力學導論 
Fundamental of Fluid Dynamics



				  博士班 



				‧電子學實驗 
Experiments on Electronics

				‧應用力學實驗 II 
Experiments on Applied Mechanics II

				 







				　







